7. International Data Transfers
If information is processed or stored outside the jurisdiction where you are located, we will take reasonable steps to protect it in accordance with applicable requirements and internal policies.

8. Children’s Privacy
Our services are intended for authorized internal use and are not directed to children. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children without appropriate authorization or legal basis.

9. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the bots or related services after any update constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.

10. Contact
